1. Run cmd node -v
2. Run  npm -v

    If you dont have these - please insstall  NODE.js on local machine

3. Insatall Angular CLI
    -npm i -g @angular/cli

4. If you try and run ng commands before installing Angular CLI
        -You will see errors 

5. To craete new appliction 
        -ng new <application_name>

6. after instaletion done to run cmd your terminal npm start or ng serve

